UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='Ah, a young $R come to speak to Sanath. What a wonderful day! I am so honored to have you grace me with your presence. Thank you!$B$BPlease... do not be so arrogant to assume my sarcasm was a compliment. Let us get one thing straight: I don\'t like you. But this little conversation doesn\'t have anything to do with us--it has to do with my master.$B$BBring me a couple hippogryph feathers for my arrows and I\'ll give you leave to see him. He\'s asked that I send adventurers to him if they proved worthy enough.' WHERE `word_id`=145636; -- locales_quest - details : entry=3381
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='Bring 2 Undamaged Hippogryph Feathers to Sanath Lim-yo in Azshara if you wish to speak to his master.' WHERE `word_id`=145637; -- locales_quest - objectives : entry=3381
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='Two feathers, just as I asked. And not bad ones at all.$B$BReady then? Just say the word and you\'re on your way.$B$BOh, and once again, mind yourself... my master doesn\'t take kindly to imbeciles, but he is very generous to those that please him.' WHERE `word_id`=145638; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=3381
