UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='The sooner we get these stinking things out of my sight and into their cage, the faster my mood will improve. I wish the Argent Crusade had given the Sunreavers the care of this creature. They\'re enough alike that they ought to be able to understand each other.' WHERE `word_id`=164705; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14090
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='Now that the coliseum is complete, the Argent Crusade has asked us to help look after the creatures that champions will be fighting.$B$BThe giant jormungar have perhaps the strangest diet; they grow strong by eating the eggs of their own kind and the best eggs come from deep jormungar.$B$BTake this drum to the Foot Steppes in central Storm Peaks and play them near the snow mounds you see there. The sound will rouse the deep jormungar. Kill them, collect their egg sacs, and return to the tournament grounds.' WHERE `word_id`=164708; -- locales_quest - details : entry=14092
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='Acquire 4 Jormungar Egg Sacs and bring them to Tylos Dawnrunner at the Argent Tournament Grounds.' WHERE `word_id`=164709; -- locales_quest - objectives : entry=14092
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='I\'ll let the crusaders know that you\'ve just returned with a fresh load of food while the Silver Covenant was sitting on its heels.' WHERE `word_id`=164710; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14092
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='I knew that Kraken was not a match for the likes of you. Without that Kraken disrupting those boats, those Kvaldir will have no choice but to retreat. Great job, Champion!' WHERE `word_id`=164715; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14095
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='Thanks to you, Kul and the aspirants will live fight the Scourge again. That\'s far from the first time someone\'s had to save Kul from himself. My only hope is that the crusaders can find a better outlet for his enthusiasm than allowing him to impart all of his bad habits to impressionable young aspirants.' WHERE `word_id`=164719; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14096
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='The kvaldir, seafaring vrykul who raid ships and coastal settlements, have overrun a tuskarr  island across the strait to the north. Their leader is a veteran raider, Drottinn Hrothgar, who seeks to control these seas.$B$BWith him in power, our shipments and troop transports will never be safe. We will be stranded here at the Lich King\'s mercy.$B$BTake this captured kvaldir war horn to the circle of tuskarr statues on the northeastern part of Hrothgar\'s Landing and use it to challenge the kvaldir leader.' WHERE `word_id`=164728; -- locales_quest - details : entry=14101
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='The defeat of the drottinn will set the kvaldir to fighting amongst themselves, buying us time to use our advantage. The crusade and the tournament are in your debt, champion.' WHERE `word_id`=164730; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14101
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='You have bought us valuable time to move against the Kvaldir and free the seas of these pests. Once again, the Argent Crusade is in your debt.' WHERE `word_id`=164734; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14102
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='Wonderful!  Another batch of powder! Just between us jewelcrafters, I\'ve been making hand over fist selling "pure titanium" jewelry to the local Dalaran mages. Even with their superior intellect, they aren\'t particularly savvy with their gold. If you get more, I\'ll be here.' WHERE `word_id`=275177; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14103
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='Ornolf the Scarred is a fearsome raider renowned among his Kvaldir brethren for raiding and capturing ships. From aboard Bor\'s Fury, he and his crew attack our ships and steal our goods.$B$BOrnolf and his men are among those who slaughtered the inhabitants of a tuskarr island to the north and renamed it Hrothgar\'s Landing. His ship sits at anchor at the eastern end of the island\'s harbor. Take this captured banner and display it on his ship to provoke him into facing you in battle.' WHERE `word_id`=164735; -- locales_quest - details : entry=14104
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='High Crusader Adelard at the Argent Tournament Grounds wants you to kill Ornolf the Scarred.' WHERE `word_id`=164736; -- locales_quest - objectives : entry=14104
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='Ornolf\'s crew will want to avenge their leader, but without him, they will be easier to defeat. We must live to carry out our mission, to see Icecrown rid of the Scourge and other evils.' WHERE `word_id`=164737; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14104
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='You are truly an example to all who have gathered beneath our banner, $N. Together, we will show the Scourge that we will not be defeated.' WHERE `word_id`=164740; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14105
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='You have done our fallen brethren a great service and spared us the need to face them again on the field of battle. As our campaign against the Scourge progresses, I find myself thinking about my own fate.$B$BShould I fall, $N, I would want someone like you to do for me what you have done for the spirits of the fallen this day. I could not bear the thought of forcing my own brothers to slay me again and again.' WHERE `word_id`=164745; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14107
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='Crusader Silverdawn wants you to mount an Argent Hippogryph, throw 6 Flaming Spears at the North Sea Kraken and take out 3 Vrykul Deepcallers.$B$BYou can find the Argent Hippogryphs right outside the Argent Crusade tent at the Tournament Grounds.' WHERE `word_id`=164750; -- locales_quest - objectives : entry=14108
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='Crusader, you may have bought those sailors just enough time to escape, Maybe next time, those Silver Covenant and Sunreavers will listen before running head first at the enemy.' WHERE `word_id`=164751; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14108
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='I\'m glad we\'ve gotten that done. It\'s not the most glorious task in the world, but when we partnered with the Argent Crusade, we promised to do all they asked of us without complaint. Of course, the same cannot be said of the Sunreavers.' WHERE `word_id`=164761; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14112
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='Great job, Champion. The fight continues, but now the Kvaldir know that we do not tolerate such attacks.' WHERE `word_id`=164767; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14136
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='Giranan the Blooded at the Argent Tournament Grounds wants you to kill 10 Kvaldir.' WHERE `word_id`=164768; -- locales_quest - objectives : entry=14140
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='Your actions have shown that we Sunreavers are far better allies to the Argent Crusade than the Silver Covenant and it is we who will be triumphant.' WHERE `word_id`=164769; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14140
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='Use the Weighted Net to capture 8 Snowblind Followers and bring them to Tylos Dawnrunner at the Argent Tournament Grounds.' WHERE `word_id`=164770; -- locales_quest - objectives : entry=14141
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='The sooner we get these stinking things out of my sight and into their cage, the faster my mood will improve. I wish the Argent Crusade had given the Silver Covenant the care of this creature. They\'re going to have to get their hands dirty when the battle for Icecrown Citadel starts and I have a feeling they\'ll prove fragile and fussy allies.' WHERE `word_id`=164771; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14141
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='Crusader Kul has gone and gotten himself into trouble again, only this time he\'s not alone. When he saw the cultists making camp at Deathspeaker\'s Watch, west of the tourney grounds, Kul gathered the aspirants for an attack.$B$BThey were easily captured, and now Kul languishes in a cage on the platform in the camp. I am sure that the cult will sacrifice the prisoners unless we can rescue them. Any of those cultists could carry keys to the black cages. Find the keys and free Kul and the captive aspirants.' WHERE `word_id`=275180; -- locales_quest - details : entry=14142
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='Kul will live to embarrass himself again. That\'s far from the first time someone\'s had to save Kul from himself. With examples like him, it\'s no wonder most of the aspirants are taking up the habits of the Silver Covenant.' WHERE `word_id`=164774; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14142
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='The Argent Crusade dispatched a fast ship carrying tallstrider meat and other supplies for us here at the tournament grounds, but it never arrived. Scouts reported seeing it attacked by the kvaldir, fearsome vrykul raiders who roam the seas.$B$BThey\'ve slain the crew and taken the cargo to an island called Hrothgar\'s Landing. If you look to the north, you can see it shrouded in the mist. Would you help us in recovering the stolen supplies? Without those tallstrider legs, we\'ll soon be out of food.' WHERE `word_id`=164650; -- locales_quest - details : entry=14143
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='Recover 10 Stolen Tallstrider Legs for Girana the Blooded at the Argent Tournament Grounds.' WHERE `word_id`=164775; -- locales_quest - objectives : entry=14143
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='These look a little worse for wear, but they\'re still edible. The crusaders will be glad to hear that we\'ve had some success. Maybe we can give the half-eaten ones to the Silver Covenant. That would make my day.' WHERE `word_id`=164776; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14143
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='I\'ve been listening to Confessor Paletress speak, and I must tell you, her words have made me think. We fight beside the crusaders, but we can learn from them, too.$B$BOff the north coast is Hrothgar\'s Landing, where the seagoing Kvaldir have overrun an old tuskarr settlement and slain the villagers. Take this book and read the rites for the dead near the corpses of the villagers. It will allow their spirits to escape the mists engulfing the island and find peace.' WHERE `word_id`=164777; -- locales_quest - details : entry=14144
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='Use the Confessor\'s Prayer Book to perform last rites for 8 Slain Tualiq Villagers and then return to Girana the Blooded at the Argent Tournament Grounds.' WHERE `word_id`=164778; -- locales_quest - objectives : entry=14144
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='<Girana accepts the prayer book from you.>$B$BThank you. We don\'t always see eye-to-eye with the crusaders, but I\'ve learned a lot from Confessor Paletress in my time here.' WHERE `word_id`=164779; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14144
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='I\'m glad we\'ve gotten that done. It\'s not the most glorious task in the world, but when we partnered with the Argent Crusade, we promised to do all they asked of us without complaint. Of course, the same cannot be said of the Silver Covenant.' WHERE `word_id`=164782; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14145
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='Very good, $N.$B$BNow, the trick is to align the facets just right...' WHERE `word_id`=164786; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14151
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='It seems things are worse than we initially thought. You still made a valiant effort and saved many of The Wavecrest\'s crew\'s lives.' WHERE `word_id`=164791; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14152
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='This is a fine list of deeds, $N!  You are to be rewarded handsomely for your accomplishments.' WHERE `word_id`=164795; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14160
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='The Horde will never be a match for our forces as long as we have people like you on our side, $N.' WHERE `word_id`=164800; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14163
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='Nothing will stand between us and total victory. For the Horde!' WHERE `word_id`=164805; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14164
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE `word_id`=164849; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14166
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='Acquire some Bread of the Dead and give it to the Cheerful Dwarf Spirit in Ironforge\'s graveyard.$B$BUse an Orange Marigold to see the otherwise invisible spirit.' WHERE `word_id`=164851; -- locales_quest - objectives : entry=14167
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc4`='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE `word_id`=164849; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14167
